@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/rag

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats

### Test Embedding
POST {{baseUrl}}/embed
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "What is artificial intelligence?"
}

### Search Documents
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "machine learning",
  "topK": 5
}

### Search Documents by Type
POST {{baseUrl}}/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "neural networks",
  "topK": 3,
  "contentType": "pdf"
}

### Full RAG Query
POST {{baseUrl}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Explain machine learning in simple terms",
  "topK": 5
}

### RAG Query with Content Type Filter
POST {{baseUrl}}/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What are the key concepts?",
  "topK": 3,
  "contentType": "text"
}

### Test Generation (direct)
POST {{baseUrl}}/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Explain quantum computing in one sentence"
}